TitleEnglish: My Daughter Left the Nest and Returned an S-Rank Adventurer
SummaryEnglish:
The life of an adventurer isn't always a glamorous one. Belgrieve finds this out the hard way when a deadly encounter robs him of his leg and the ability to pursue his dreams not long after setting off for fame and fortune. But fate isn't finished with this retired adventurer!
While gathering herbs in the wilderness, he discovers an abandoned baby girl and names her Angeline after deciding to raise her as his own. Angeline grows up to become a top-tier adventurer in her own right, yet after venturing out into the world and making a name for herself, fame, fortune, and power hold no allure for the accomplished S-rank adventurer: her heartfelt wish is for nothing more than to see her father again.
Aliases: Bōkensha ni Naritai to Miyako ni Deteitta Musume ga S-Rank ni Natteta
Boukensha ni Naritai to Miyako ni Deteitta Musume ga S-Rank ni Natteta
Boukensha ni Naritai to Miyako ni Deteitta Musume
My daughter grew up to "Rank S" adventurer.
My Daughter Left the Nest and Returned an S-Rank Adventurer

1.SummaryEnglish: Angeline, the Black-Haired Valkyrie, longs for nothing more than a vacation to return to her home in the countryside and visit the father who taught her everything she knows about adventuring...but getting there will be an adventure all its own.

2.SummaryEnglish: Although Angeline has yet to make it home, tales of her deeds are reaching her father in the countryside. The noble Bordeaux family is also eagerly seeking out Belgrieve to show their gratitude after Angeline rescued their youngest sister.

3.SummaryEnglish: Angeline still hasn't been able to make it home to see her father. So when the local guild master tells her all that's standing between her and some time off is a potentially legendary monster, you can bet she's up for the challenge.

4.TitleEnglish: Quiet Days in Turnera With the Occasional Family Spat
4.SummaryEnglish: Angeline finally makes it back home with her friends in tow, but Belgrieve can hardly believe his ears when he hears how she introduces him. If Angeline says he's the Red Ogre and he says he's not, then which story is really true?

5.SummaryEnglish: Father and daughter are finally reunited after five long years, so Angeline isn’t ready to be separated from Belgrieve just yet when a job comes in for him. She and her friends thus decide to tag along to Bordeaux, where an unexpected problem awaits.

6.SummaryEnglish: Belgrieve has caught wind of a plot brewing in Bordeaux, and the dark clouds roiling over the estate are a portent of things to come.

7.TitleEnglish: A Long Night and a Bright Dawn

8.TitleEnglish: Meeting the Inhabitants of the Woods
8.SummaryEnglish: Belgrieve is back at home, but trouble abounds even outside of Bordeaux. This "trouble" just happens to be a rogue elven princess who's out for demon blood.

9.TitleEnglish: Father and Daughter Meet New People
9.SummaryEnglish: Belgrieve continues to handle the trouble that's cropped up in the countryside. Meanwhile, Angeline stumbles upon trouble of her own in the city.

10.SummaryEnglish: After their encounter in the city, Angeline takes on two surprising wards. Protecting people she cares about, however, turns out to be much harder than she ever expected.

11.SummaryEnglish: Belgrieve and Angeline begin to enjoy the changes in their lives, but there's change on the horizon for them both. Will they cross paths again as they set out on new journeys?

12.SummaryEnglish: Angeline makes her grudging journey to the capital and quickly learns nobles are not to be underestimated. Meanwhile, Belgrieve has begun looking for something he thought he lost long ago.

13.SummaryEnglish: Angeline is in the capital to be honored, but she continues to struggle with the very idea. Belgrieve also continues to grapple with his past.
